      <title>日本石破茂面临预算紧缩问题，并会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/japan-s-ishiba-faces-crunch-over-budget-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂周五在议会开幕时寻求对其少数派政府的支持，他计划通过创纪录的 115.5 万亿日元（7380 亿美元）年度预算，并处理与美国新政府的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/japan-s-ishiba-faces-crunch-over-budget-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
